or: #000000; border-bottom-style: none !important; background-color: transp=
arent !important; display: inline-block;">
<span>[5]</span>
</a>=C2=A0Modern finance is=C2=A0very interested in efficiency, and abhors =
the idea of buying anything, putting it in a box, and=C2=A0<em>doing nothin=
g with it</em>. You=E2=80=99ve got some stuff in a box, you take it out of =
the box, you=C2=A0<em>lend=C2=A0</em>it to someone who wants to do somethin=
g with it, and you earn interest.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The Satoshi Nakamoto vision of crypto was very=
 different: This idea of building opaque leverage into every part of the sy=
stem, of constructing everything on webs of debt, is part of what Bitcoin w=
as reacting against.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">But the modern vision of crypto, or at least t=
he 2022 vision of crypto, was like everything else in finance. You could ho=
ld Bitcoins in your digital wallet, like holding $100 bills in your regular=
